{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"672","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"台電近百億投資台南光電 今夏併網","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: '>2020-04-10 16:07</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: '><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E5%8F%B0%E5%8D%97%E5%A4%AA%E9%99%BD%E5%85%89%E9%9B%BB.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 400px;' />&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: '>台電台南太陽光電場裝置容量達<span lang='EN-US'>15</span>萬瓩，預計今年<span lang='EN-US'>8</span>月底前全數併網，每年可發<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>億度綠電。（台電提供）</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>〔記者林菁樺／台北報導〕台電投入<span lang='EN-US'>96.5</span>億元資金在台南將軍及七股區鹽灘地建置台灣最大規模、裝置容量達<span lang='EN-US'>150MW</span>（<span lang='EN-US'>15</span>萬瓩）的單一太陽能電廠，今（<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>）日搶先將<span lang='EN-US'>40MW</span>光電併入電網運轉測試，預計於今年<span lang='EN-US'>8</span>月底前全數併網，未來每年將可發出<span lang='EN-US'>2</span>億度綠電，提供超過<span lang='EN-US'>5.5</span>萬戶家庭年用電量，同時每年可減碳達<span lang='EN-US'>8</span>公噸。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>台電表示，台南地區為台灣早期曬鹽重地，長年日照充足，利用台南市將軍區及七股區等已未產鹽之鹽灘地，投入<span lang='EN-US'>96.5</span>億元資金打造<span lang='EN-US'>214</span>公頃、相當於<span lang='EN-US'>300</span>座足球場大小，總裝置容量達<span lang='EN-US'>150MW</span>（<span lang='EN-US'>15</span>萬瓩）的鹽田太陽光電場，將佔目前全台太陽光電裝置容量<span lang='EN-US'>4%</span>。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>台電指出，台南鹽田光電場全區使用超過<span lang='EN-US'>46</span>萬片高效率太陽能板，並在場址內設計綠色圍籬及生態池，規劃鳥類棲息友善環境，希望可兼顧電力開發與生態保育永續。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>台電除在台南建置全台最大的鹽田光電場，也持續推動自有建物屋頂型光電及與它單位合作進行水面型的光電設施，目前台電運轉中的總裝置容量已累計達<span lang='EN-US'>123MW</span>；另外台電在彰化外海跟海風借電，離岸風電一期計畫裝置容量約<span lang='EN-US'>110MW</span>，預計年底前併聯發電。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: '>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3129596</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-04-13","clk_count":"207"}},"__N_SSG":true}